Package: debiasLLMReporting
Type: Package
Title: Debiased Inference for LLM-as-a-Judge Evaluations
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Yiqun", family = "Chen", email = "yiqun.t.chen@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given = "Moran", family = "Guo",
           role = "aut"))
Description: Methods to correct for measurement error when using LLM judges to
    evaluate model outputs. Implements PPI, PPI++, Rogan-Gladen, and EIF
    estimators for debiased prevalence estimation with confidence intervals.
